uk.thecodingbadgers.minekart.racecourse

Class RacecourseLap

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.thecodingbadgers.minekart.racecourse.Racecourse
      • uk.thecodingbadgers.minekart.racecourse.RacecourseLap

  • public class RacecourseLap
extends Racecourse
    Author:
    TheCodingBadgers A standard race where jockeys must complete a given number of laps of a course. There are a given number of checkpoints. A jockey must go through all checkpoints in the correct order, once a jockey has passed through the last checkpoint the given number of laps they are the winner
